Happy earth day!! 🌏❤️ help make every day earth day, and find ways to live a more sustainable lifestyle. You can have shorter showers, be conscious of food waste, turn off the lights when leaving the room, unplug electronics when not in use, and incorporate more sustainable recipes to create a healthier environment. Especially with more prominent issues with our environment like pollution, garbage in the oceans and climate change, it’s so incredibly important to live everyday with the earth in mind. It’s our beautiful home and we must protect it 💙✨make a positive impact in the environment

#planetearth #planetearth🌎 #saveourhome #livesustainably #happyearthday🌎 #makeeverydayearthday #fightfortheplanet #protect #cleantheoceans #planttrees #environmentallyfriendly

Successful flower sale on Friday ❤️ all proceeds from the sale will be donated to support women and children find resources to get out of abusive relationships. It’s so incredibly important for everyone to feel safe and loved, and get the help that they need. Every change, small or large, makes a difference in the world, and we hope to be a part of that change. ✨💙 #love #beautiful #wegeneration #metowe #wegroup #bethechange #change
